high_descs: Look down at the sink.
Pick up the knife on the ledge of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the knife in the green cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup.
Turn right and walk back to the sink.
Place the cup in the left part of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it in a sink.

high_descs: Move a step to your right, so you're directly in front of the rightmost sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter in front of the sink.
Turn left and carry the knife to stand in front of the counter space between the stove and toaster.
Place the knife in the green cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup with the knife inside from the counter.
Turn and carry the cup and knife to stand in front of the two sinks.
Place the cup and knife in the leftmost sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife in a cup in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the sink on your left.
Pick up the knife in front of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the left with a green cup on it.
Put the knife in the green cup.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn right and walk to the sink on your left.
Place the cup with the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the green cup with the knife in it in the sink.
